StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetProspectProfessedExamById]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@ExamId uniqueiden..er
AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT ProspectProfessedExamId, ProspectId, ProspectProfessedExamType, Score1, Score2, Score3, PiCatMmScore, PiCatGtScore, PiCatElScore, PiCatClScore, ExamDate, ExamEnteredDate, LastUpdateUserId FROM [USMC].ProspectProfessedExam
WHERE ProspectProfessedExamId = @ExamId
END
